Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他将作为GN-001的驾驶员…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.52,0:00:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下  皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还是个孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员特性已经达到基准值了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吠陀选上他的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是有相当的思想准备才加入组织  成为Gundam Meister的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.16,0:00:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟年龄没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代号是洛克昂·斯托拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连大气层外的目标都能狙击的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想用Gundam来改变世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.87,0:00:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是哦  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·斯托拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·斯托拉托斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普特利麦奥斯发来了特别密码消息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:02:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么内容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与联合国军搭载了拟GN Drive的MS部队开始了交战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界会向哪一边倾斜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是联合国  还是他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:21.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你一直在地上  战力才会分散的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他非死不可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人还在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空发牢骚  不如来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  抱歉  菲露特  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是哈罗的错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗用不着道歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事  真讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,27台中只回来了11台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕获到的机体也丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  Gundam的新能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马内金上校  我建议从当前宇宙域撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照目前这样下去  只会无意义地折损兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么想的  不过联合国司令部说要派增援部队过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增援？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说GN Drive搭载型还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令是在其抵达后开始第二次攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到朝着本舰过来的GN-X
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幸存者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体核对确认
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机师是隶属AEU的帕特里克·克拉萨乌少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起  上校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,净让人担心  傻小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长翅膀的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有受到我的脑量子波的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采取过切断措施了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样  一定要在下次战斗中做个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是完全体的超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能输给未完成的实验体E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照指示  在散布GN粒子的同时吹动了卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这能瞒过敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小行星周围在监视范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  能采取的措施需要全部使出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  Gundam的情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.83,0:05:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios只要拆除了飞行单元就能出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue在拆下外装后也能以Nadleeh出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也准备了专用武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多久才能完成？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也要8小时吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6小时  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:05:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以目前的战力  能指望的只有强袭用货柜  Exia和GN Arms
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一可依赖的TRANS-AM也有时间限制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇·李·诺瑞加  请你提供下一个作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你想去战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能把敌方的拟GN Drive搭载型消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以向世界展示我们的力量  并继续计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风险太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人可能会派增援…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这不光是我一个人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Meister的一致意见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷路亚和刹那也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活下去的觉悟…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿尔·萨谢斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙把洛克昂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的双亲和妹妹是在KPSA的自杀炸弹式恐怖袭击中丧生的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我为家人报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我报仇雪恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不顾自身安危而报了仇吗  洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊  你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:30.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是冒犯神明的行为哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在死亡的终点处…不存在神明！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being…我们存在本身不就有意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在本身…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背负着对已故人们的思念  而面对世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要以我自己的意志来面对  而不是神明的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第34观测班发来了消息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认有四个物体正在逐渐远离小行星带
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让小行星带周围巡哨部队去确认
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佯动作战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  应该是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机影从后方接近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  这机体是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是从Celestial Being那里接收来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那他们选择了战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  只能行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么呢  菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写信？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是给在天国的爸妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特你的双亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不吉利啊  遗书什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他们「暂时无法相见  对不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种气势  菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为和洛克昂约定过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要遵守哦  这个约定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊～我要不也写封信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要写给谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是给殖民地的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是养母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么美好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了逃避而离家出走  被吠陀选中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人收信也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  里希特你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父母是轨道电梯的技术人员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我小时候因太阳光纷争就那样了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的情况都不简单呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为这样  大家才会加入Celestial Being啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  像这样彼此交谈  这还是第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为有保守秘密的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nadleeh的整备怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  以既没有审判系统  粒子储藏量又小的Nadleeh…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此也要行动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须要替洛克昂报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要太急躁为好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特·格雷斯  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给洛克昂写了封信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  你想给谁写信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:11:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会寂寞的…是它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  哈罗  你要待在他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在洛克昂·斯托拉托斯的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂  洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去吧  哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E传感器有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到敌方部队  相对速度…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离可能的战斗区域还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方部队总共有多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是13台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  其中有个相当庞大的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示在显示屏上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…是战斗舰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…搭载了拟太阳炉的MA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子光束过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那种距离！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一粒子出力部中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把粒子供给全部转到第二出力部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二波  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭货柜出击  目标  敌MA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭货柜  出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特  把托勒密开到附近的卫星的阴影里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios和Nadleeh由货柜直接出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照作战  对太空船进行两方向同时攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:09.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机  以卫星为掩护接近进行攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头功就归本大爷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方出现高速接近的机影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敌机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给Alvatore就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要做个了断！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌MS部队由左右包抄而来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想再接近了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭你这个半裸的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离用TRANS-AM还早…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台机体是…你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:13:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊  阿雷路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…还不想死啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验体E-57！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入射程了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样才会有那种输出功率…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密被…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普特利麦奥斯被…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死  是谁！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三  第四货柜严重受损
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右侧受损严重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降下E20至68的隔舱板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  医务室…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随便就这么去了啊…混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统出现故障
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field无法张开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去强袭货柜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去迎击的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联系伊恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nadleeh  对目标…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.95,0:16:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是幸运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是为了计划…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.13,0:16:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是为了洛克昂！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些蠢蠢欲动的家伙们！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没干掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  要击中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames的太阳炉有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接状况好像有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那种数据…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  这样下去会被干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是骗她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有1台朝这边过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想再挨菲露特骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想绕到死角里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让他得逞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将货柜从托勒密分离
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:17:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯！  里希提！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯  里希提
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回话  克里斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希提…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:19:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和父母一起被卷了进去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体有一半就是这种感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是活着呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是死了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希提…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身边不是就有这么好的男人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…真没眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希提
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希提！  请回话  克里斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希提呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特…在？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更注意下妆扮啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括洛克昂那部分  也要一并活下去啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了…要改变世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希提！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜·西尔纳——！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.05,0:21:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击不起作用！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就直接撞过去！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.34,0:21:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用直接攻击好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.12,0:21:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.71,0:21:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的伊奥里亚·修亨贝格的亡灵们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亚历桑德罗·柯纳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要将你们作为通往新世界的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.36,0:21:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.44,0:22:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱逐目标！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.15,0:23:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios坠落了  Nahleeh坠落了  Exia坠落了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生与死逐渐交错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.83,0:23:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「刹那」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.79,0:23:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从破坏到重生的变革期
